snippet.title: StackHoops - Gameplay Demo - Now On Steam
snippet.description:
Play NOW on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2357750/StackHoops/

StackHoops is a casual multiplayer basketball-like game. Play against your friends, random matchmaking, or against the computer. Customize your ball, court, and more to showoff to the world and win in style. Complete challenges and prove your skills!

VerseRoll on iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/verse-roll/id6450562374
